node.text:
👨‍✈️✈️ Do you wish to become a pilot in the United States , convert your ICAO/EASA license to FAA or become a flight instructor to build 1500+ flight hours, join US regional airlines and start earning as a pilot?
✅Pelican Flight Training is the place to be!!
We offer professional pilot programs, individual courses, exceptional time building packages & instructor training to local and international students for both airplane and helicopter training. 🌏International students may have the opportunity to practice in the US to build 1500+ hours and improve their professional skills as an FAA certified instructor.
✈️Contact us to get started on this new exciting career!
@flighttrainingschool
